    {
      "id": "structural-expansion-contract",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Runtime Contract",
      "position": {
        "x": -60,
        "y": 120
      },
      "width": 340,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Runtime Contract\n\nWhen `mode=expand`:\n- resolve target graph and requested entry surface\n- project only branch-safe nodes and edges\n- strip document-scoped system nodes\n- do not merge remote authority into host context\n- mark imported entities with projection metadata",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
