    {
      "id": "structural-expansion-phases",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Implementation Phases",
      "position": {
        "x": 340,
        "y": 120
      },
      "width": 380,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Implementation Phases\n\n### Phase 1: Projection Normalizer\n- classify system nodes and execution-bearing nodes\n- strip or suppress them during expansion\n- preserve structural nodes and edges\n\n### Phase 2: Entry Surface Resolver\n- support graph-level `open` / `expand` handles\n- resolve handle -> node id with fallback chain\n\n### Phase 3: Execution Boundary\n- disable remote scripts/views/plugins by default in projected nodes\n- preserve provenance and trust metadata\n\n### Phase 4: UX + Validation\n- show clear warning when expanding a document-scoped graph\n- expose `Open at` / `Expand from` in document properties",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
