      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Remaining Questions\n\n- Which node types are stripped versus downgraded?\n- Should remote editor/node views be fully blocked or selectively allowed?\n- How should entry surfaces be stored in manifest/settings?\n- What warning text best explains document vs branch behavior?",
