    {
      "id": "structural-expansion-acceptance",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Acceptance Criteria",
      "position": {
        "x": 220,
        "y": 520
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- Expanding a full task/document graph does not import a second manifest, legend, or dictionary\n- Host graph execution context remains unchanged after expansion\n- Imported branch is visibly attached and collapsible\n- Port `navigate` still opens the full document graph\n- Entry handles select the intended expansion start without raw internal node ids\n- Validation warnings explain downgraded/stripped content clearly",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
